{"id":367066,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2014/10/輔仁媒體【多圖】從tvb看不到的龍和道警民衝突過/","date":"2014-10-17T09:20:53Z","modified":"2017-02-19T03:46:59Z","title":"輔仁媒體｜【多圖】從TVB看不到的龍和道警民衝突過程","content":"<p>10月16日凌晨，金鐘龍和道凌晨再有佔領市民以快閃方式攻佔馬路，警方移走障礙物恢復行車後，約二百人仍聚集在龍和道兩旁行人道，警方不時警告市民不要再衝出馬路。期間，偶爾有市民掉零錢到馬路上再拾起，警方勸籲後又返回行人道，間歇導致有車輛要停低或慢駛。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1701b-650x433.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-367087\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1701b-650x433.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_1701b-650x433\" width=\"575\" height=\"383\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1701b-650x433.jpg 650w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1701b-650x433-300x199.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 575px) 100vw, 575px\" /></a></p>\n<p>情況持續到約凌晨一時半，一名男子疑因將水樽掉出馬路，擊中一輛途經車輛，一名便衣警員、一名警長及一名督察上前欲將之拘捕，男子跑入添馬公園逃走，三警當中的便衣警員將男子壓在花槽邊制服。數十名市民包圍三名警員，要求解釋拘捕原因，質問跌水樽構成什麼罪行。警長拔出警棍指向市民，警告他們不要靠近。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1710b-650x433.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-367088\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1710b-650x433.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_1710b-650x433\" width=\"575\" height=\"383\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1710b-650x433.jpg 650w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1710b-650x433-300x199.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 575px) 100vw, 575px\" /></a></p>\n<p>市民繼續要求解釋，數分鐘後突然有人從後推擠，該警長及督察見狀便用警棍猛打四周的市民及記者。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1745b-650x433.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-367089\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1745b-650x433.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_1745b-650x433\" width=\"575\" height=\"383\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1745b-650x433.jpg 650w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1745b-650x433-300x199.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 575px) 100vw, 575px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1752b-650x433.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-367092\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1752b-650x433.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_1752b-650x433\" width=\"575\" height=\"383\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1752b-650x433.jpg 650w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1752b-650x433-300x199.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 575px) 100vw, 575px\" /></a></p>\n<p>數分鐘後人群退後一段距離，被捕男子被便衣警員完全壓在地上，警長及督察繼續舉警棍戒備。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1764b-650x433.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-367093\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1764b-650x433.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_1764b-650x433\" width=\"575\" height=\"383\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1764b-650x433.jpg 650w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1764b-650x433-300x199.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 575px) 100vw, 575px\" /></a></p>\n<p>約十分鐘後，數名持圓盾警員前來增援，市民擋住企圖不讓警員內進，雙方推擠一輪後增援警員成功進入圈內。有增援警員呼喝警告市民不要再碰到他。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1775b-650x433.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-367094\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1775b-650x433.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_1775b-650x433\" width=\"575\" height=\"383\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1775b-650x433.jpg 650w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1775b-650x433-300x199.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 575px) 100vw, 575px\" /></a></p>\n<p>未幾有更多機場特警從馬路走向天馬公園增援，前進時舉起胡椒噴霧，近馬路的市民後退。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1957b-650x433.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-367100\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1957b-650x433.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_1957b-650x433\" width=\"575\" height=\"383\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1957b-650x433.jpg 650w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1957b-650x433-300x199.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 575px) 100vw, 575px\" /></a></p>\n<p>增援警員進入及市民後退令人群向花槽位置擠湧，花槽邊的警察於是用圓盾將市民向外推，並用警棍打人，人群激烈推撞。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1814b-650x433.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-367095\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1814b-650x433.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_1814b-650x433\" width=\"575\" height=\"383\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1814b-650x433.jpg 650w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1814b-650x433-300x199.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 575px) 100vw, 575px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1868b-650x433.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-367096\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1868b-650x433.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_1868b-650x433\" width=\"575\" height=\"383\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1868b-650x433.jpg 650w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1868b-650x433-300x199.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 575px) 100vw, 575px\" /></a></p>\n<p>花槽旁邊的人被擠壓得透不過氣，有人慘叫，部分人爬到花槽上暫避。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1913b-650x433.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-367098\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1913b-650x433.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_1913b-650x433\" width=\"575\" height=\"383\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1913b-650x433.jpg 650w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1913b-650x433-300x199.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 575px) 100vw, 575px\" /></a></p>\n<p>花槽邊的警察繼續揮動警棍，該督察更轉身用警棍擊打在花槽上暫避的市民及拍攝中的記者。(本網記者幸剛巧將袋子揹在身前，沒被警棍直接擊中身體。)</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1926b-650x433.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-367099\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1926b-650x433.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_1926b-650x433\" width=\"575\" height=\"383\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1926b-650x433.jpg 650w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1926b-650x433-300x199.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 575px) 100vw, 575px\" /></a></p>\n<p>陸續有戴頭盔警察從馬路向公園推進，市民向公園方向後退。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1972b-650x433.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-367101\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1972b-650x433.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_1972b-650x433\" width=\"575\" height=\"383\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1972b-650x433.jpg 650w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1972b-650x433-300x199.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 575px) 100vw, 575px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1981b-650x433.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-367102\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1981b-650x433.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_1981b-650x433\" width=\"575\" height=\"383\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1981b-650x433.jpg 650w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1981b-650x433-300x199.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 575px) 100vw, 575px\" /></a></p>\n<p>警察推進期間突然施放至少兩輪胡椒噴霧，數十名市民及記者被噴中。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1993b-650x433.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-367103\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1993b-650x433.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_1993b-650x433\" width=\"575\" height=\"383\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1993b-650x433.jpg 650w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1993b-650x433-300x199.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 575px) 100vw, 575px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1995b-650x433.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-367104\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1995b-650x433.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_1995b-650x433\" width=\"575\" height=\"383\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1995b-650x433.jpg 650w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_1995b-650x433-300x199.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 575px) 100vw, 575px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_2012b-650x433.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-367105\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_2012b-650x433.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_2012b-650x433\" width=\"575\" height=\"383\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_2012b-650x433.jpg 650w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_2012b-650x433-300x199.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 575px) 100vw, 575px\" /></a></p>\n<p>人群向公園內再後退，被捕男子亦早已被帶上警車，警方向馬路撤去。被噴中的人在路邊沖洗，未有中胡椒噴霧的市民向馬路方向前進。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_2021b-650x433.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-367106\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_2021b-650x433.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_2021b-650x433\" width=\"575\" height=\"383\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_2021b-650x433.jpg 650w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_2021b-650x433-300x199.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 575px) 100vw, 575px\" /></a></p>\n<p>警方在馬路與行人路間設防線，舉起紅旗警告，市民停在行人道邊與警方對峙。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_2022b-650x433.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-367107\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_2022b-650x433.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_2022b-650x433\" width=\"575\" height=\"383\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_2022b-650x433.jpg 650w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_2022b-650x433-300x199.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 575px) 100vw, 575px\" /></a></p>\n<p>警方在龍和道兩邊設防線戒備，東西行線各有一條行車線停用。市民坐行人道戴著裝備戒備。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_2035b-650x433.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-367108\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_2035b-650x433.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_2035b-650x433\" width=\"575\" height=\"383\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_2035b-650x433.jpg 650w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_2035b-650x433-300x199.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 575px) 100vw, 575px\" /></a></p>\n<p>一段時間後，雙方愈來愈鬆散，愈來愈多人坐低休息。接下來幾個小時人群漸散去。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_2049b-650x433.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-367109\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_2049b-650x433.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_2049b-650x433\" width=\"575\" height=\"383\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_2049b-650x433.jpg 650w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/IMG_2049b-650x433-300x199.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 575px) 100vw, 575px\" /></a></p>\n<p>對是次警民衝突now有較完整的報導︰ http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=115146</p>\n<p>作為參考，TVB是這樣報導的︰ http://news.tvb.com/local/543ef8316db28ceb2a000001/</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&amp;id=b4fd4ae247\" method=\"POST\"><a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><input id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" style=\"display: block;\" name=\"EMAIL\" required=\"\" size=\"25\" type=\"email\" value=\"\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" /><br />\n<input id=\"in_post_subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" name=\"subscribe\" type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" /></form>\n","author":1002,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,9203],"tags":[12719,32464,13468,10707,11881,19948,25921,23755]}